112
00:12:33,050 --> 00:12:36,800
Ale v skutočnosti nastalo zatmenie mesiaca..

113
00:12:36,800 --> 00:12:42,710
Až v druhej polovici noci bolo vidieť trocha svetla.

114
00:12:42,710 --> 00:12:45,700
Zatmenie čo začalo...

115
00:12:47,630 --> 00:12:52,500
